profile: At Bakers Furniture, our experienced craftsmen manufacture and finish solid wood furniture and cabinetry in our shop.  We will work with you to create your custom kitchen, wall unit, fireplace surround, office furniture and bathroom vanities.  We also manufacture solid wood furniture for every room in your home.
